The Altiplano, on the highway from La Paz to Cochabamba; ca 96 km. SE from the La Paz tollbooth. Small pond. Growing in the shallows (.1-.2 m). Abundant. This pond is fairly deep, with a soft, silty bottom. It appears to be spring fed and has a small outflow. pH = 6.4. Surrounding vegetation: Puna

Laguna Toro; adjacent to the road to Estanica Caliente. Area: ca 3.5 ha. (ph = 8.1) Growing throughout the shallows. Frequent. Many individuals were in fruiting condition. The lake possesses a very shallow basin, has an inlet and an outlet, seemingly with year-round flow, and is possibly secondarily eutrophic. Vegetation type: Puna.
